Variation.
Female MUSM 8959 is larger in size (
35.6 mm
), and EW is narrower than the IOD (wider in the holotype). The two postrictal tubercles are also present. Coloration is the same as in the holotype. In life (
Figure 8
), bluish black coloration under arms and above groin, more conspicuous than in male holotype.
